rComments: This prof appears to have no idea what she's teaching, to the point where she thought this class had a tutorial and last minute realized that there wasn't when she already submitted the grading criteria to the faculty. She gives no indication out of what she wants of you in assignments, and it appears she has no clue what she's doing.

I'm not sure how they let her teach this course. She read off the jot-notes on the slides made by the Professor who designed the course (which means she often read grammatically incorrect gibberish without realizing it half the time). Her assignments also are super unclear. I think it would be better if she gave the course her own spin.
